OL,4,CPost Office after more than 40 years
OL,6,FThe closure of the sub post office
OL,7,Fleaves a hole in village life.
OL,9,FCustomer after customer told ITV Cymru
OL,10,FWales that the loss was devastating
OL,11,Ffor them.
OL,13,FAnn Wilkinson said it meant everything
OL,14,Fto the community.
OL,16,F"Everybody is gutted that it is
OL,17,Fclosing," she said. "It should have
OL,18,Fbeen here forever."
