OL,6,FThe closure means that it won't be
OL,7,Fjust a matter of popping down the road
OL,8,Fto get cash out or send and receive
OL,9,Fparcels.
OL,11,F"But they have earned a happy
OL,12,Fretirement," she said.
OL,14,FOne lady said: "I just don't know what
OL,15,FI will do.
OL,17,F"When you come here there is always a
OL,18,Ffriendly chat and help when you need
OL,19,Fit."
