OL,4,CPost Office after more than 40 years
OL,6,FAnother customer added: "It is another
OL,7,Fnail in the coffin of village life. It
OL,8,Fis very sad."
OL,10,FDennis said the turbulence surrounding
OL,11,Fthe industry had scared people off
OL,12,Ffrom the idea of buying into the
OL,13,Fbusiness.
OL,15,FDennis continued: "It is the best
OL,16,Fthing you can do for a living, but it
OL,17,Fshould award you a living, but it
OL,18,Fdoesn't. You can lose a lot of money
OL,19,Fvery quickly. Times have changed."
