OL,6,FHe believes there are also bigger
OL,7,Fissues at stake with people moving
OL,8,Faway from using cash, a trend he
OL,9,Fstrongly believes is a negative one
OL,10,Ffor individuals and society in general.
OL,12,FHe has been thanked by the Post Office
OL,13,Ffor his long service. They have wished
OL,14,Fhim a well-earned retirement.
